&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl8zODI0NDE3NC9hcnRpY2xlL2RldGFpbHMvMTM2OTcwMzUzP2FwcF92ZXJzaW9uPTYuMy4xJmFtcDtjb2RlPWFwcF8xNTYyOTE2MjQxJmFtcDtjc2RuX3NoYXJlX3RhaWw=&#34;&gt;快速入门 Kotlin①基本语法 - CSDN 博客&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
